data.description: Can you imagine having a home in Mililani for under $500k? Look no further. This 2 bedroom one bath home in Mililani is what you're looking for. Enjoy your luxury vinyl flooring and the convenience of a full-size stacked Samsung washer/dryer as well as a large refrigerator with water and ice dispenser. Catch some sun on your balcony, and when you've had enough, cool off in the home by using your AC. If you really want to cool off, feel free to use your community pool. If salt water is needed, the North Shore and its beautiful beaches are within reach. This is your time to establish yourself in the desired town of Mililani. Monthly Tax amount is based on the 2023 assessed values.
